import React from 'react'
import Admin from './Admin'
import {
    BrowserRouter as Router,
    Switch,
    Route,
    Link
  } from "react-router-dom";
function Master() {
  return (
        <Router>
      <Navbar />
      <Admin />
      <Switch>
          <Route path="/about">
            <About />
          </Route>
          <Route path="/users">
            <Users />
          </Route>
          <Route path="/">
            <Home />
          </Route>
      </Switch>
    
    </Router>
  )
}

export default Master
